APPLICATION
     crypto - The Crypto Application

DESCRIPTION
     This chapter describes the application Crypto in OTP,  which
     provides message digests MD5 and SHA, and CBC-DES encryption
     and decryption.

     The purpose of this application is to provide message digest
     and DES encryption for SMNPv3.

